Do you need private access to AWS Services (like S3, Secrets Manager)?
→ Yes → Use PrivateLink

Do you need to expose your service to other accounts securely?
→ Yes → Use PrivateLink

Do you need full VPC-to-VPC communication?
→ Yes → Use VPC Peering or Transit Gateway

Do you need scalable multi-VPC routing?
→ Yes → Use Transit Gateway

Do you want to access 3rd-party SaaS securely?
→ Yes → Use PrivateLink
